-- Flight Centre set to buy Liberty Travel: source
-- 
-- Sun Nov 11, 2007 5:47pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/11/us-flightcentre-liberty-idUSSYU00347220071111

 

 MELBOURNE  (Reuters) - Australian travel firm Flight Centre Ltd ( FLT.AX ) is planning to buy U.S. travel retailer Liberty Travel, a source familiar with the situation said on Monday, confirming a newspaper report. 

 The Australian Financial Review reported the $135 million deal would triple the size of Flight Centre's North American business. (Reporting by  Victoria Thieberger )